# Unit Testing
Always prefer the MCP tools to run unit tests:
* `mcp_ignition-mcp_launch_unit_test_ginkgo_focus` for Ginkgo tests.
* `mcp_ignition-mcp_launch_unit_test_name` for non-Ginkgo tests.

# E2E Testing
Always prefer the MCP tools to run E2E tests:
* `mcp_ignition-mcp_launch_e2e_test_odh_rhoai` for E2E tests.

## Upstream (kserve)
Utilizes Github Actions from .github/workflows/e2e-test.yml 

## Downstream (odh-rhoai)
Utilizes Openshift CI operator from 
https://github.com/openshift/release/tree/master/ci-operator/config/opendatahub-io/kserve
Specific configuration (master): https://github.com/openshift/release/blob/master/ci-operator/config/opendatahub-io/kserve/opendatahub-io-kserve-master.yaml